.' => 'ሲነቃ Fluid Checkout ከተሰኪው ጋር ተኳሃኝነት የተመቻቹ ቅጦችን ይተገበራል። ለ Stripe የክፍያ ቅጽ መስኮች ብጁ ቅጦችን እየተጠቀሙ ከሆነ ይህንን ማሰናከል ይፈልጉ ይሆናል።','Theme Nyture' => 'ጭብጥ Nyture','Output the checkout steps section from the Nyture theme when using Fluid Checkout.' => 'Fluid Checkout በሚጠቀሙበት ጊዜ የፍተሻ ደረጃዎች ክፍሉን ከናይture ጭብጥ ያውጡ።','Maybe be forced as "required" if the billing address section is displayed after the shipping address section, and the billing phone field is set as "required. This is needed to ensure the shipping address can be copied to the billing address when that option is checked.' => 'ምናልባት የመክፈያ አድራሻ ክፍሉ ከማጓጓዣው አድራሻ ክፍል በኋላ ከታየ፣ እና የክፍያ መጠየቂያው ስልክ መስኩ “አስፈላጊ” ተብሎ ከተዋቀረ “አስፈላጊ” ተብሎ ሊገደድ ይችላል። ይህ አማራጭ ሲረጋገጥ የመላኪያ አድራሻው ወደ የክፍያ መጠየቂያ አድራሻ መገልበጥ መቻሉን ለማረጋገጥ ያስፈልጋል።','Maybe be forced as "required" if the billing address section is displayed after the billing address section, and the billing phone field is set as "required. This is needed to ensure the billing address can be copied to the billing address when that option is checked.' => 'ምናልባት የክፍያ መጠየቂያ አድራሻ ክፍሉ ከሂሳብ አከፋፈል አድራሻ ክፍል በኋላ ከታየ እንደ &quot;አስፈላጊ&quot; ሊገደድ ይችላል, እና የሂሳብ አከፋፈል የስልክ መስኩ &quot;አስፈላጊ ነው. ይህ አማራጭ ሲፈተሽ የመክፈያ አድራሻው ወደ የክፍያ መጠየቂያ አድራሻ መገልበጥ መቻሉን ለማረጋገጥ ይህ ያስፈልጋል.','Allows customers to make payments for orders that are either created manually by the store admin or not completed during checkout.' => 'ደንበኞች በመደብሩ አስተዳዳሪ በእጅ ለተፈጠሩ ወይም በፍተሻ ጊዜ ላልተጠናቀቁ ትዕዛዞች ክፍያ እንዲፈጽሙ ይፈቅዳል።','The plugin WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers is not compatible with Fluid Checkout' => 'ፕለጊኑ WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers ከ Fluid Checkout ጋር ተኳሃኝ አይደለም።','Company name field for billing address' => 'የኩባንያ ስም መስክ ለክፍያ መጠየቂያ አድራሻ','Change visibility for the company name field for the billing address section on the checkout form.' => 'በቼክ መውጫ ፎርሙ ላይ ላለው የክፍያ መጠየቂያ አድራሻ ክፍል ለኩባንያው ስም መስክ ታይነትን ይቀይሩ።','Theme Bookshelf' => 'ጭብጥ የመጽሐፍ መደርደሪያ','Output the checkout steps section from the Bookshelf theme when using Fluid Checkout.' => 'ፈሳሽ ቼክአውትን በሚጠቀሙበት ጊዜ የፍተሻ ደረጃዎች ክፍልን ከመጽሃፍ መደርደሪያው ጭብጥ ያውጡ።','Account password' => 'የመለያ ይለፍ ቃል','An account will be created with the information provided at checkout when completing the order.' => 'ትዕዛዙን ሲያጠናቅቁ ተመዝግበው ሲወጡ ከተሰጠው መረጃ ጋር መለያ ይፈጠራል።','Choose the style of the progress bar.' => 'የሂደት አሞሌውን ዘይቤ ይምረጡ።','Bars' => 'ቡና ቤቶች','Theme Ireca' => 'ጭብጥ ኢሬካ','WooCommerce page layout' => 'WooCommerce ገጽ አቀማመጥ','Force wide layout on WooCommerce pages' => 'WooCommerce ገጾች ላይ ሰፊ አቀማመጥን አስገድድ','This ensures the content section is not too narrow on WooCommerce pages including checkout, cart, order received, order pay and account pages.' => 'ይህ በ WooCommerce ገፆች ላይ የይዘት ክፍሉ በጣም ጠባብ እንዳልሆነ ያረጋግጣል፣ ቼክ መውጫ፣ ጋሪ፣ የተቀበሉት ትዕዛዝ፣ ክፍያ ማዘዣ እና የመለያ ገጾች።','Button label for applying coupon codesApply' => 'ያመልክቱ','Checkout step titleContact' => 'ተገናኝ','Checkout step titleShipping' => 'መላኪያ','Checkout step titleBilling' => 'የሂሳብ አከፋፈል','Checkout step titlePayment' => 'ክፍያ','Checkout substep change link labelChange' => 'ለውጥ','Checkout substep save link labelSave changes' => 'ለውጦችን ያስቀምጡ','Substep review textNone.' => 'ምንም።','Substep review field format%1$s' => '%1$s','Substep review field format: with label%2$s: %1$s' => '%2$s፡ %1$s','Image uploader.No image selected.' => 'ምንም ምስል አልተመረጠም።','Settings sectionCart' => 'ጋሪ','Settings sectionOrder pay' => 'ክፍያን ማዘዝ','Settings sectionThank you' => 'አመሰግናለሁ','Settings section titleIntegrations' => 'ውህደቶች','Settings section titleLicense keys' => 'የፍቃድ ቁልፎች','Captcha positionBefore place order section' => 'የትዕዛዝ ክፍል በፊት','Captcha positionBefore place order button' => 'የትዕዛዝ አዝራር በፊት','No shipping method chosen label for the order summary--' => '--','Close button aria-labelClose' => 'ገጠመ','Log in link label at checkout contact stepLog in' => 'ግባ','Log in separator label at for when guest checkout is disabledOr continue below' => 'ወይም ከታች ይቀጥሉ','Log in separator label at for when guest checkout is disabledOr continue as a guest' => 'ወይም እንደ እንግዳ ቀጥል','Clear image selection on admin pages.Remove image' => 'ምስል አስወግድ',] ];